 you and your little (or not so little) ones make decorations. Crafting mat
 erials provided.  \n  \nCoffee\, water and snacks provided.   \n  \n**RAIN
  OR SHINE!!**  \n  \n**Questions? Contact**  \nShomrei Office\, (973) 746-
 5031  \nopen-door@shomrei.org\n\n
