UID:TU1889728569
DTSTAMP:20260313T210315Z
SUMMARY:Sukkot Your Way
DESCRIPTION:### **Sukkot Your Way - on Erev Sukkot**\n\n  \nEveryone is inv
 ited to participate by requesting a seat in someone's Sukkah or by offerin
 g to host either in your personal Sukkah or in the Sukkah at Shomrei. Rabb
 i Julie and Justus will be hosting as well as a number of other Shomrei fa
 milies.  \n  \nIf you'd like to participate\, email to shabbatyourway@shom
 rei.org **by Monday\, September 29 at noon.** Specify how many people\, ag
 es of children\, the latest start time\, and any allergies or pets. We wil
 l do our best to accommodate everyone.  \n  \n**Questions?**  \nContact th
 e Shabbat Your Way Team  \nshabbatyourway@shomrei.org: http://shomrei.org/
 \n\n
