UID:TU1925222156
DTSTAMP:20260313T210315Z
SUMMARY: From Bach to Blues
DESCRIPTION:Please join us for a musical Sunday afternoon with congregants 
 Laura Kaufman on cello\, Steve Kamin on piano and Elliott Fischer on guita
 r and vocals. Laura and Steve will perform Jewish-themed pieces influenced
  by the Golden Age of Jewish Cantorial music and play some Bach. In the se
 cond half of the program\, Elliott\, who has taught classes on the Blues\,
  will perform blues songs and explain how rock musicians were influenced b
 y the Delta Blues.   \n  \nLight snacks and coffee will be served during t
 he performance  \n  \n$10 Cost to Attend.   \n  \nRSVP at: https://shomrei
 .easyshul.com/events/68c9a27cce7fdb0026ff36c3  \n  \n**Questions?**  \nCon
 tact Melissa Mehl  \nOperations Manager  \nmmehl@shomrei.org  \n(973) 746-
