SUMMARY:Shabbat Your Way
DESCRIPTION:Whether in your own home or someone else’s\, with one person 
 or many\, having an elaborate meal or ordering take-out\, there is not one
  way to celebrate Shabbat. “Shabbat Your Way” is an opportunity to cul
 tivate a Shabbat mindset in a way that feels right for you. Shomrei will p
 rovide resources and ideas to help you add something new or special to you
 r Shabbat practice or gathering.  \n  \n**Shabbat Your Way Schedule (4th F
 riday of each month):** July 11\, July 18\, Sept 26\, Oct 24\, Nov 28\, De
 c 26\, Jan 23\, Feb 27\, Mar 27\, Apr 24\, May 22\, June 26\n\n
