BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:TU1944451649
DTSTAMP:20260313T210315Z
SUMMARY:A German Jew’s Triumph: Fritz Oppenheimer and the Denazification 
 of Germany 
DESCRIPTION:A German Jew’s Triumph: Fritz Oppenheimer and the Denazificat
 ion of Germany   \nBook Talk and Presentation with Cindy and Harry Handler
   \n  \nJoin us for an engaging presentation by local author Cindy Handler
  and her husband Harry Handler about Cindy’s new book\, A German Jew’s
  Triumph: Fritz Oppenheimer and the Denazification of Germany.   \n  \nFri
 tz Oppenheimer\, Harry’s grandfather\, was a scion of a privileged banki
 ng family and a decorated WW I soldier in the German army who built a succ
 essful international law practice in Germany but fled Berlin right before 
 Kristallnacht. When he came to the U.S.\, he entered basic training for th
 e army and quickly rose to become Eisenhower’s chief legal aide and tran
 slator ultimately playing a key role in taking top Nazi leaders into capti
 vity and transforming Germany into a sustainable democracy. The Handlers w
 ill present samples of the original documents and fascinating journals and
  letters kept by Fritz and his wife that they used as the basis of their r
 esearch.\n\nThis program is in commemoration of Kristallnacht\, the "Night
  of Broken Glass\," a state-sponsored anti-Jewish pogrom carried out by th
 e Nazi regime in 1938.\n\n  \n**Questions? Contact**  \nShomrei Office\, (
 973) 746-5031  \nopen-door@shomrei.org\n\n
LOCATION:Social Hall
CATEGORIES:Events
