UID:TU1992135903
DTSTAMP:20260313T210315Z
SUMMARY:Adult Wine & Dine at Marcel
DESCRIPTION:  \n**Adult Wine &amp\; Dine at Marcel - Sunday\, Dec 6 at 7:30
 PM**  \n  \n  \nCome wine &amp\; dine with your Shomrei crew at a local Mo
 ntclair favorite! Join us for an Adults Night Out with dinner\, drinks\, a
 nd a conversation about Israeli food culture and how it’s shifted over g
 enerations with fellow Israeli\, and Marcel co-owner\, Daniel Ben Zeev. He
  will be sharing interesting tidbits about how Israeli cuisine has continu
 ously shifted as the country has become a melting pot for Jews of all back
 grounds. Shomrei to supply soft drinks and wine\; BYO any other favorite b
 everage.  \n  \n  \n$20 per person  \n  \nOpen to all adults in the Shomre
 i community  \n  \nSpace is limited (max. 50 people)\, so please RSVP asap
 .\n\n
LOCATION:Marcel Bakery and Kitchen
CATEGORIES:Events
