SUMMARY:Midday MeetUp - Jersey Tomato
DESCRIPTION:**Midday Meetup - Jersey Tomato  \n  \nA monthly gathering to m
 ake connections and learn together.  \n11:45am Catered Lunch (free)  \n12:
 30pm Featured Program   \n  \nFood historian\, Judith Krall-Russo\, will t
 alk about where the tomato originated and why it became one of New Jersey
 ’s favorite crops\, the history of the tomato industry in New Jersey\, a
 bout heirloom varieties\, modern hybrids and the folklore attached to toma
 toes.  \n  \n**Cost:** FREE or Suggested Donation of $10 per person to off
 set costs. (Bill My Account is only open to Shomrei Members)  \n  \n**RSVP
 :** Required so we know how much food to buy.  \nhttps://shomrei.easyshul.
