BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:TU2020599871
DTSTAMP:20260313T210315Z
SUMMARY:Untangling Israel's Government
DESCRIPTION:**Why is Israel's political system so complex?** Join us for a 
 conversation on the complexities of Israel's political system with Daniell
 a Gefen\, the Israeli "shlicha" at the Jewish Federation of Greater MetroW
 est. An educator\, clinical social worker\, and community activist\, Danie
 lla brings years of experience working across diverse communities and fost
 ering bridge-building initiatives in Jerusalem.  \n  \nSponsored by the Sh
 omrei Israel Committee  \n  \n**rsvp required: https://shomrei.org/israel*
 *  \n  \nQuestions?  \nContact Daniella Gefen at  \ndgefen@jfedgmw.org\n\n
LOCATION:Social Hall
CATEGORIES:Events
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
SEQUENCE:0
