 rent artists exhibiting in the gallery. The program will start partway thr
 ough kiddush. Grab a bite and join us in the gallery.  \n  \n**Gallery Vis
 its** The Shomrei Community can view the exhibit whenever the building is 
 open. (Bring your fob.) Unaccompanied visitors\, by appointment only. Cont
 act: gallery@shomrei.org\n\n
