BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:TU2042067998
DTSTAMP:20260313T210315Z
SUMMARY:Interfaith Inclusion Conversation
DESCRIPTION:Join Rabbi Julie and President Aaron Delaney in a series of dis
 cussions around the Interfaith Community.\n\nRabbi Julie will be hosting a
  series of three community meetings in February and March\, where she will
  present background information about interfaith families\, including abou
 t the demographics of our community and the policies of the Conservative M
 ovement on this issue. Participants in these meetings will be invited to g
 ive input and engage in dialogue with the Rabbi\, Aaron Delaney\, and with
  other members of the community as we share perspectives around this topic
 .\n\nBabysitting will be available at the Sunday sessions upon request (em
 ail Aviva Arad aarad@shomrei.org).\n\nThe dates of the Community Meetings 
 are as follows:\n\nSunday\, February 22\, 10:00 – 11:30am\n\nTuesday\, M
 arch 3\, 8:00 – 9:30pm\, Zoom Only (https://shomrei.org/z\\_rabbijulie: 
 https://shomrei.org/z_rabbijulie)\n\nSunday\, March 22\, 1:00 – 2:30pm a
 t the social hall\n\nPlease remember to bring your fob to access the build
 ing.\n\n
CATEGORIES:Events
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
SEQUENCE:0
