SUMMARY:Midday MeetUp - Musical Afternoon with Laura and Elliott
DESCRIPTION:**Midday MeetUp - A Musical Afternoon with Laura and Elliott  \
 n  \nA monthly gathering to make connections and learn together.  \n11:45a
 m - Catered Lunch   \n12:30pm - Music starts  \n  \nJoin our wonderful Sho
 mrei musicians Laura Kaufman on cello and Elliott Fischer on guitar with v
 ocals for an afternoon lunch and concert.  \n  \nRSVP required so we know 
 how much food to buy.   \nRSVP: https://shomrei.easyshul.com/events/695574
 6dc573c10026160e34  \n  \nVoluntary donations are welcome to cover the cos
 ts of the program. Suggested donation $10 per person.   \n  \nPlease remem
 ber to bring your fob to access the building.  \n  \nFull_Season_Schedule_
 for_Midday_MeetUps: https://shomrei.org/calendar/midday-meetup-calendar  \
 n  \n**Questions?**  \nContact the Shomrei Office  \noffice@shomrei.org  \
 n(973) 746-5031  \n  \n\\#middaymeetup\n\n
