UID:TU2058495218
DTSTAMP:20260313T210315Z
SUMMARY:Yom HaShoah Interfaith Remembrance
DESCRIPTION:All are welcome to join the annual interfaith Yom Hashoah Holoc
 aust commemoration\, hosted by the Montclair Interfaith Clergy Association
 .  \n  \nAs part of the service\, we will hear from Pamela Romanchuk\, gra
 nddaughter of four Holocaust survivors\, who will share her family's stori
 es of survival\, family\, legacy\, and the enduring strength of the Jewish
  people.  \n  \n**Questions?**  \nContact Bnai Keshet  \n(973) 746-4889\n\
 n
LOCATION:Bnai Keshet\, 99 S Fullerton Ave\, Montclair\, NJ 07042\, USA
CATEGORIES:Events
CLASS:PUBLIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
SEQUENCE:0
